    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border-dark space-y-4">
      <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
        This website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute an offer to sell or a solicitation to buy any security. Investments in real estate involve risk. Past performance is not indicative of future results.
